Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.33,0:00:04.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:08.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I bring you marvelous illusions that \Nmake this town sparkle at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.16,0:00:12.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy the miracle that happens \Naround a stage heroine tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:21.16,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1)}Marth and Rosa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.62,0:00:21.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Everyone! This theater \Nfinally opens tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:26.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's also opening day for {\i1}Marth and Rosa{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:32.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's the day our mortal enemy, Kid the \NPhantom Thief, says he's going to appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:37.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Our duty this time is to protect \Nthe world's largest emerald,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.62,0:00:44.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Green Dream, as it's being used \Nfor tomorrow's performance only!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:47.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:51.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down, \Neven among fellow officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's a master of disguise!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.21,0:01:01.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He may already be here right now, \Nposing as one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:06.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, part-timer! A little help over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:08.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.39,0:01:14.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All right! I'm going to deploy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.64,0:01:19.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Teams 1 and 2 take the first floor \Nfront lobby and the lobby gallery.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:24.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How many officers did you bring here, \NInspector Nakamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:31.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But that suits \NKid the Phantom Thief just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:29.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Team 3, the 4th-floor lounge. \NTeams 4 and 5, the fountain plaza.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:34.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:38.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You can't even get through these short lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:40.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:44.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to disgrace my \Nperformance with your lousy acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:46.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,N-No, I would never...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:51.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, Reiko. Megumi-chan isn't \Nused to being on stage yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:53.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You don't need to get that mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:56.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're just as bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.49,0:01:59.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Even though you're playing the prince, \Nyou fumble your lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:02.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's only when you throw in \Ntoo many ad libs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:04.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:06.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm the heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.24,0:02:08.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All of you should just focus on \Nmaking me look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:12.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Or rather, the tour de force \Nof Reiko Imaizumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:20.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It seems further rehearsing \Nwouldn't do any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.06,0:02:21.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:25.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the rest to you, fearless leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.78,0:02:28.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Reiko-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:30.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,P-Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:34.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I won't mess up anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:36.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I promise I'll do my best,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:38.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,so please, let's practice once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.52,0:02:43.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're Megumi Furuhata-san, I believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:45.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:49.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You have no talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:53.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You can't be an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.29,0:02:55.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It'd be better if you gave it up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:57.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Reiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:03.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sheesh. What a disgusting woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:06.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:09.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The only daughter of this theater's owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:14.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Even though she used her parent's pull to \Nland that part, she lords it over everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:18.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,When I think that she's the heroine, \Nit makes me want to take up a different trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:24.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I hope Kid the Phantom Thief \Nwrecks the whole show.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:05:01.95,Signs - Thief Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}Green Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.95,0:05:05.96,Signs,,0,0,0,,Marth and Roza\N0 days until the show opens
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:03.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Good job, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:05.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:09.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid! You wanna go out drinking with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:12.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No, I've still got a few...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:15.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...tricks to prepare for tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:17.97,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Electric Room
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:24.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That being said, with all the cops around,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:26.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't do what I need to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:28.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is a pretty pickle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.62,0:05:34.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Marth-sama, Marth-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:34.99,Signs,,0,0,0,,Main Hall Stage Entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:41.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Whither are you, Marth-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.99,0:05:45.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Please, throw that name away right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:46.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Who's here this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:51.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Okay. If that is your wish, \NI'll be happy to dispose of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:56.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Oh! Marth-sama! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.51,0:05:58.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Why did you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:06:01.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}If you're found here, \Nyou're as good as dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:06.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's the girl who got chewed out \Nbefore during rehearsal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:06.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Oh, no! My father's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:08.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:09.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Who are you?! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:10.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,She's doing all the parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:13.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Go! Run away, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:17.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Even if the wings of my love are torn off,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:19.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I shall return to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:27.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not a weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:29.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm a part-timer! Just a part-timer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:32.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I was making props, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:37.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,U-Um, look...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.61,0:06:40.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about plays,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:44.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but that was pretty great just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:46.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:51.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,With your skill, they should \Ngive you a better part.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:57.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm no good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:07:02.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,When I'm in front of people, \NI feel weak at the knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:06.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I get scared. Everyone's looking at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:12.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I feel like they see right through me \Nand are ridiculing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:15.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Thanks to that, I keep flubbing lines...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:18.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Even though this is the first time \NI've gotten a role with lines,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:21.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm a nuisance to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:25.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm really not \Ncut out to be an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:27.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A radish could out-act me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:34.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Try a pumpkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:37.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,P-Pump...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:40.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Everyone's like that in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:42.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But after you get used to it, you don't \Neven notice the eyes of the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:46.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's like they say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:51.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Think of the audience as \Nrows of pumpkins in a field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:56.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll try!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:01.50,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}The Next Day
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:04.64,Signs,,0,0,0,,Marth and Roza
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:15.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful theater!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:18.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And it's got a retractable roof, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:23.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's Tamura-san, the actor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:27.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Look! Anan's here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:32.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wow! Celebrities everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:35.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If that girl had this one's personality,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:37.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,she wouldn't have any hassles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}I can't wait, you know, Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:41.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What kind of expression is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:46.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted to see the play, \Nso I had my dad get us complimentary tickets!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:49.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's see a little more \Ngratitude on your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:51.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:55.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Electric room, sound off! Any abnormalities?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:58.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The power and wiring are fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.36,0:08:59.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:03.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Taking advantage of a blackout to \Nsteal is a common tactic of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:06.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Stay alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:06.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:13.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All right. At least we won't \Nlose power in the theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:15.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And even if we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:22.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,the 20 battery-powered lights we \Nset up will keep him in our sights!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:27.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid, this is your last appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:32.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You'll never get the chance \Nto escape from me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:33.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:36.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Megumi Furuhata, Megumi Furuhata...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.53,0:09:37.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:41.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Furuhata Megumi... "Servant A."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you laughin' at?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:49.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,After all, it's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:53.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That you wanted to see a play like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:56.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The setting is Europe in the Middle Ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:10:00.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A prince and princess from two \Ncountries that are enemies
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:04.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,overcome various obstacles \Nto be together in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:07.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's a totally romantic story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:09.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.51,0:10:13.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And now you're embarrassed! How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:16.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have come here with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:21.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:25.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We now present {\i1}Marth and Rosa{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:33.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:38.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I've searched all over the country, but no \Nwoman here would make me a suitable wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:42.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Isn't she out there somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:45.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Beautiful, sweet,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:49.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and dazzling like this Green Dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:52.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,the royal family treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:15.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid didn't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:21.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No, but there's one more scene where the \Njewel's shown, so it'll be out of our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:24.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He'll probably make a play for it then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:29.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A ball to choose the queen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:33.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh... Hosted by Prince Marth of Gaia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:37.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,D-Don't do it, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:39.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gaia is our country's enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:42.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If you're discovered, \Nwho knows what would happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:44.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Megumi-chan's on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:47.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Please think better of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:51.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then are you saying that I, \Nthe most beautiful woman in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:55.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,should be shut away in this \Ncountry for the rest of my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:12:01.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,U-Um, I-I wasn't saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:05.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Reiko's suddenly ad-libbing again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:08.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Never mind. You can be excused.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:17.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't have a good feeling \Nabout that heroine...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:18.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:22.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:24.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Did you want to ruin the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:26.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,N-No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:30.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're an eyesore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:33.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Get out of my sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:38.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Reiko-san! You're on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:51.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You don't have anything to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:54.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault, Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:56.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on, cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:12:59.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's almost the last scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:01.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's go backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.56,0:13:04.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:17.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, beautiful one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:21.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I hope you will become my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:24.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It cannot be, Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:27.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A relationship between us is forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:33.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If you would have it, I would give you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:39.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...the Gaia royal family's treasure, \NGreen Dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:42.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All right, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:44.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Where are you gonna come from, Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:48.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to hide \Nin the dark tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:53.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're naive, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:57.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Darkness isn't the only thing \Nthat can hide a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:04.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,L-Lights?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:11.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:23.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-The jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:27.10,Signs,,0,0,0,,The emerald is mine!\N- Kid the Phantom Thief
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.10,0:14:31.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Y-You... I didn't think you'd use \Nbright lights to disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:33.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and lock down \Nall entrances and exits!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:35.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's still in the theater!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:38.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector! What about the electric room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:42.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Leave it! All hands gather!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:45.45,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Electric Room
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:56.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:15:03.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,After the curtain of night closed in\N and the moon began to tilt,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:07.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,there was still one girl in the palace \Nafter everyone had left the ball,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:11.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and she was in love with the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:13.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Her name...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:16.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...was Servant A!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:24.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,She had been bullied every day\N by the mean princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:28.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...and couldn't tell anyone \Nhow she felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:32.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This lovely girl just \Nendured the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:34.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,in her small chest, \Nlike that of a baby bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:38.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-These cheesy lines...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:52.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But then a strange magician...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:56.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...appeared from above...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:00.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...and alighted before her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.61,0:16:06.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,K-Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:09.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,K-Kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:13.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:16.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm just a magician who'll make...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.64,0:16:20.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...your dream come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:27.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I stole this jewel, just as I\N stole the light...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.18,0:16:33.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...but it seems it's not \Nwhat I was looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:37.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's keep this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:40.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...on your beautiful finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:46.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, it's time, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:49.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Go to your prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:57.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.46,0:16:59.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:02.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:04.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:07.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Director! Should I lower the curtain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.97,0:17:10.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No, leave it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:13.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Pumpkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.98,0:17:18.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You mustn't escape the audience's gaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:22.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Muster courage and accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:27.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No one can see through to your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:30.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:32.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:18.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,S-She's singing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:20.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:47.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh! What a beautiful singing voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:49.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It feels as if my mind is clear\N for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:51.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,M-Marth-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:55.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come, let me see your face more clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:57.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What a pretty young woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:01.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.65,0:19:06.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...so this moment won't escape me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.70,0:19:16.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, let's continue with the play!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:18.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes! For Megumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:03.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I didn't know the story \Nwould be this beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.02,0:20:05.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I wonder if that was the real \NKid the Phantom Thief before?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.73,0:20:07.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You know, Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:10.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:12.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That had to be an actor, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:16.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But what a great play!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:19.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm glad I got to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.63,0:20:22.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.29,0:20:47.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector, I wonder why Kid \Ndidn't make off with the jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.17,0:20:49.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How would I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.65,0:21:02.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Megumi-san's in another magazine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.83,0:21:06.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,She been famous ever since that play.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.94,0:21:10.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I hear she's gonna be \Nin a TV drama next.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.38,0:21:13.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But there's something \NI don't like about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:15.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:21.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, after all, her ideal man \Nis Kid the Phantom Thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.23,0:21:28.66,Signs,,0,0,0,,Megumi Yoshida\NExclusive Interview\NMy ideal man is Kid the Phantom Thief
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.84,0:21:26.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:35.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Tonight, a nameless servant
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:39.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,became a dazzling star \Nin the space of a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.66,0:21:43.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Everyone is the main character \Nof their own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.08,0:21:45.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course, that goes for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:50.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, see you next illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.44,0:23:23.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Boy, Megumi-chan had a \Nbeautiful singing voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.98,0:23:26.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I wish I could have listened to her \Nforever, but who's got the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.57,0:23:28.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The next treasure's waiting for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.12,0:23:31.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Who's calling me an amateur?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.48,0:23:33.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It seems you've got confidence \Nin your own thieving ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:36.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but it wouldn't be wise\N to underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.11,0:23:38.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I accept your challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.11,0:23:43.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Next time on {\i1}Magic Kaito 1412{\i0}: \NGolden Eye (Part One): Chat Noir's Challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.11,0:23:43.24,Signs,,0,0,0,,Golden Eye (Part One):\NChat Noir's Challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.68,0:23:46.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Step right this way! Watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.58,0:23:48.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't miss the illusion!
